Eddie Ryder https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Eddie_Ryder 0 Eddie Ryder (January 23, 1923 – March 29, 1997) was an American television and film actor, as well as a writer and television director. Ryder was born in New York City and died in El Paso, Texas.
